## General
error.general = Something went wrong, sorry.
error.invalid.json = Invalid Json Format.

## Login
login.invalid.credentials = Username or password are incorrect!
login.logged.out = You logged out successfully!

## Users
msg.user.created = User has been created!
email.not.available = Email address not available. Please choose another one!
user.not.logged = You should be logged to access this resource!

## Movies
msg.movie.added = Movie has been added to your Watchlist!
msg.movie.deleted = Movie has been removed from your Watchlist!

